â€œYes, in healthcare it is mandatory to protect PII, especially PHI. Regulations like HIPAA require that any data that can identify
a patient must be secured â€” whether itâ€™s names, dates of birth, addresses, 
or medical record numbers. If we fail, the organization risks legal penalties, loss of trust, and compliance violations.â€


